Detailed Description

template<class TYPE>
class gaia::base::List< TYPE >

The class implements circular bi-directional linked list data structure.

It implemets circular bi-directional linked list operation methods. List possesses an access point, whcih is forwardly linked head and backwardly linked tail of list. Usually, it is used with ListIerator.

See also:
ListIterator
 // Create a list
 gaia::base::List<gaia::base::String> lst;
 
 // Insert two strings into list at head.
 lst.insert(lst.begin(), String::valueOf(2011));
 lst.insert(lst.begin(), String::valueOf(2012));
 
 // Delete string "2012".
 lst.erase(lst.begin());
